  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS OF YAZOO COUNTY, MISSISSIPPI, TO ESTABLISH AN ECONOMIC AND INDUSTRIAL DEVELOPMENT AUTHORITY TO BE KNOWN AS THE YAZOO ECONOMIC PARTNERSHIP; TO PROVIDE FOR THE APPOINTMENT OF TRUSTEES OF THE PARTNERSHIP; TO PROVIDE THE POWERS AND DUTIES OF THE PARTNERSHIP; TO PROVIDE THAT THE PARTNERSHIP MAY BE AUTHORIZED BY THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS TO PROVIDE CERTAIN ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AND/OR INDUSTRIAL DEVELOPMENT FOR THE COUNTY AND THE MUNICIPALITIES LOCATED THEREIN; TO AUTHORIZE THE BOARD OF SUPERVISORS TO DISSOLVE THE YAZOO COUNTY ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT DISTRICT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
